      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented V&V history; version-controlled simulation scripts; audit trail for all simulation runs.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 used with documented release notes and patch history. All case files version-controlled in institutional GitLab repository. Run logs retained with checksums confirming reproducibility across three independent re-runs."
