      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver passes relevant benchmark problems from published literature; manufactured solution or order-of-accuracy test documented.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verified against FDA nozzle benchmark (Hariharan et al. 2011) with second-order spatial accuracy confirmed via manufactured solution test. Order of accuracy p=1.97 observed, consistent with nominal second-order scheme."
