      "acceptanceCriteria": "GCI < 5% on fine-medium mesh pair for hemolysis index QoI at all operating points.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.2M cells). Richardson extrapolation applied per Celik et al. (2008). GCI fine-medium pair ranged 2.1%–3.9% across all five operating points, exceeding the acceptance threshold. Asymptotic convergence ratio confirmed (ratio 0.98–1.03)."
