      "rationale": "Reynolds-averaged Navier-Stokes (RANS) with SST k-omega closure is the established approach for blood pump CFD per published literature and FDA benchmark studies. Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2; literature precedent accepted as justification."
    },
